<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_1746242d376b.aspx"><b>鸳鸯</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson1746242d376b">
<p>鸳鸯于飞，毕之罗之。君子万年，福禄宜之。<br />鸳鸯在梁，戢其左翼。君子万年，宜其遐福。<br />乘马在厩，摧之秣之。君子万年，福禄艾之。<br />乘马在厩，秣之摧之。君子万年，福禄绥之。</p>
</div>
</div>
